sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Platform Operator
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Reconciler as ModelRegistryReconciler<br/>(in-process watch)
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Gateway as Data Science Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant MR as model-registry REST<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over User,PG: Flow 1: Model Registry Instance Provisioning
        User->>K8sAPI: Create ModelRegistry CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI->>Reconciler: Watch event (CR created)
        Reconciler->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment<br/>(model-registry + kube-rbac-proxy)
        Reconciler->>K8sAPI: Create Service, Route,<br/>HTTPRoute, RBAC, NetworkPolicy
        Reconciler->>K8sAPI: Update CR status<br/>(Available/Progressing conditions)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Client,PG: Flow 2: REST API Access (kube-rbac-proxy + Route)
        Client->>Router: GET /v1/model_registry/<br/>TLS 1.2+
        Router->>KRBP: Forward request<br/>TLS reencrypt to 8443/TCP
        KRBP->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(can user GET services?)
        K8sAPI-->>KRBP: Allowed
        KRBP->>MR: Forward to localhost:8080<br/>HTTP (pod-internal)
        MR->>PG: Query metadata<br/>5432/TCP Configurable SSL
        PG-->>MR: Query results
        MR-->>KRBP: JSON response
        KRBP-->>Router: HTTPS response
        Router-->>Client: JSON response
    end

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over Client,PG: Flow 3: REST API Access (Gateway API)
        Client->>Gateway: GET /model-registry/{name}/<br/>TLS 1.2+ Platform auth
        Gateway->>KRBP: HTTPRoute forward<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS (URL rewrite)
        KRBP->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(can user GET services?)
        K8sAPI-->>KRBP: Allowed
        KRBP->>MR: Forward to localhost:8080<br/>HTTP (pod-internal)
        MR->>PG: Query metadata<br/>5432/TCP Configurable SSL
        PG-->>MR: Query results
        MR-->>KRBP: JSON response
        KRBP-->>Gateway: HTTPS response
        Gateway-->>Client: JSON response
    end
